      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHAMPLAIN (1) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten half a length, (34.52) at this track. One of the contenders. QUINLEE BALE (4) is a talented type progressing through the grades and building a strong record. Has been on speed to score at her last couple of runs. Last start won this track in a handy 29.39 beating Zipping Fiyero. Sure to measure up. REGAL KADE (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at Sale over 640m behind Emerald Downs (39.58) in a Restricted WIN. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Should be in this for a long way. MAKE THEM CRY (3) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
